message: Key to success: Use the ğŸŒ¡ï¸ growth serum on *every* item, both individual ingredients and combined hybrids, as it consistently increases value. Always combine items that share the *same* 'lives in' feature (e.g., two water creatures) to create new hybrids. *Never* combine items that live in different environments (e.g., water + land + air), as this leads to severely negative-valued 'overcomplicated' items.
